{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NDcy_0022","text":"不愛她說下去亦無味","structure":{"line_index":22,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情的無趣","失去意義"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["不愛","無味"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,4,3,4,2,4,2,0,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bat1","oi3","taa1","syut3","haa6","heoi3","jik6","mou4","mei6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"不愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"她","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"說","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"下去","pos":"PART"},{"text":"亦","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"無味","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"此句表達了不愛時的感受，一切都變得索然無味，語氣帶有厭倦。"},"source":{"title":"愛一個人","artists":["陳慧琳"],"lyricists":["李克勤","林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_472","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NDcy_0021","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5oWn55Cz_NDcy_0023","paragraph_id":"para_07"}}
